## Randomization works in expectation | *La randomisation fonctionne en moyenne*

$$
\begin{aligned}
ATE = \overline{\tau_i} &= \overline{Y_i(1)-Y_i(0)} \\
&= \overline{Y_i(1)}-\overline{Y_i(0)}
\end{aligned}
$$

